"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:2.14.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">2.14.2</span> 標題：箭（arrow）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בֵּן, אַשְׁפָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ben ’ashpah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:13\">LAM 3:13</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בֵּן, קֶשֶׁת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ben qesheth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:20\">JOB 41:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： חֵץ, חֵץִי</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： chets, chetsi)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:23\">GEN 49:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:8\">NUM 24:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:23\">DEU 32:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:42\">DEU 32:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:7\">1SA 17:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:20\">1SA 20:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:21\">1SA 20:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:21\">1SA 20:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:22\">1SA 20:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:36\">1SA 20:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:38\">1SA 20:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:15\">2SA 22:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:15\">2KI 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:15\">2KI 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:17\">2KI 13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:17\">2KI 13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:18\">2KI 13:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:32\">2KI 19:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:2\">1CH 12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:15\">2CH 26:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:4\">JOB 6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:6\">JOB 34:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:14\">PSA 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:2\">PSA 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:15\">PSA 18:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:3\">PSA 38:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:6\">PSA 45:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:5\">PSA 57:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:8\">PSA 58:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:8\">PSA 58:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:4\">PSA 64:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:8\">PSA 64:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:18\">PSA 77:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:5\">PSA 91:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps120:4\">PSA 120:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:4\">PSA 127:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:6\">PSA 144:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:23\">PRO 7:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:18\">PRO 25:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:18\">PRO 26:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:28\">ISA 5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:24\">ISA 7:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:33\">ISA 37:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:2\">ISA 49:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:7\">JER 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:9\">JER 50:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:14\">JER 50:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:11\">JER 51:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:12\">LAM 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:16\">EZK 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:26\">EZK 21:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:3\">EZK 39:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:9\">EZK 39:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:11\">HAB 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:14\">ZEC 9:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַטֶּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mateh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:9\">HAB 3:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： רֶשֶׁף</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： reshef)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps76:4\">PSA 76:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： βέλος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： belos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:16\">EPH 6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis5:12\">WIS 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir19:12\">SIR 19:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir26:12\">SIR 26:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:51\">1MA 6:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc5:3\">2MA 5:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc12:27\">2MA 12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Odes2:23\">ODA 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Odes2:42\">ODA 2:42</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σχίζα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： schiza)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc10:80\">1MA 10:80</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： τόξευμα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： toxeuma)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:30\">2MA 10:30</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Latin</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">拉： sagitta</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd16:7\">2ES 16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd16:13\">2ES 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd16:16\">2ES 16:16</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/UBS-0015_arrow.jpg\" alt=\"箭\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">箭 (© Deutsche Bibelgesellschaft, Stuttgart by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>箭是一支纖細的直桿，用蘆葦或木材製成，長約50—70厘米（20—28英吋）。箭的一端固定有一個石頭或金屬做的尖頭，另一端則切出一個凹槽，好嵌入弓弦。箭的凹槽端有時會綁上兩根或更多根羽毛，使射出的箭在飛行時更加穩定。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.14.1 弓 (bow)&lt;REALIA:2.14.1&gt;</a> 。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希伯來文<em>reshef</em> 通常指一些燃燒著的或者像火一樣的東西（如火花、閃電等；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:7\">JOB 5:7</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:48\">PSA 78:48</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song8:6\">SNG 8:6</a> ）。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps76:4\">PSA 76:4</a> （《和》76:3），這個詞與「弓」平行，很可能指某種燃燒著的箭。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:13\">LAM 3:13</a> ：參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.14.3 箭袋、箭囊 (quiver)&lt;REALIA:2.14.3&gt;</a> 中的註解。</p>\n<p>希伯來文<em>mateh</em> 通常指杆、棍棒或牧羊人的杖（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.2.4 竿、木棍、牧羊杖 (rod, club, shepherd’s staff)&lt;REALIA:1.2.4&gt;</a> ），但在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:9\">HAB 3:9</a> 中，很多譯本將這個詞譯為「箭」（“arrows”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Hebrew Old Testament Text Project (UBS)\">HOTTP</abbr> 和《〈那鴻書〉、〈哈巴谷書〉和〈西番雅書〉手冊》［<em>A Handbook on The Books of Nahum, Habakkuk, and Zephaniah</em> ］支持這種譯法。）這節經文的希伯來原文非常含糊。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
